\"ngram\": \"the Scotsman\", \"from\": 773, \"to\": 785}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Everyone gets really antsy in these first rounds, because of all the build-up, the hype, and it's a big stadium with lots of people.\", \"from\": 792, \"to\": 925, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Everyone\", \"from\": 793, \"to\": 801}, {\"ngram\": \"these first rounds\", \"from\": 823, \"to\": 841}, {\"ngram\": \"all the build-up\", \"from\": 854, \"to\": 870}, {\"ngram\": \"the hype\", \"from\": 872, \"to\": 880}, {\"ngram\": \"a big stadium\", \"from\": 891, \"to\": 904}, {\"ngram\": \"lots\", \"from\": 910, \"to\": 914}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 918, \"to\": 924}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So I just made sure I stayed relaxed, and when it was time to go I put the burners on.\", \"from\": 927, \"to\": 1014, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 982, \"to\": 986}, {\"ngram\": \"the burners\", \"from\": 999, \"to\": 1010}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Maybe a little bit too hard, I thought everyone was going to be battling me.\", \"from\": 1015, \"to\": 1091, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 1054, \"to\": 1062}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But it felt exactly how I thought it would, and that's always a reassuring thing.\\\"\", \"from\": 1092, \"to\": 1174, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a reassuring thing\", \"from\": 1154, \"to\": 1172}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kerr produced a stunning performance to take World Championship gold in Budapest last year, ahead of Norway's reigning Olympic champion Jakob Ingebrigtsen.\", \"from\": 1176, \"to\": 1331, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1248, \"end\": 1256, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"score\": 0.9751438622232768, \"rank\": 0.025489713608143505, \"text\": \"Budapest\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\"}, {\"begin\": 1277, \"e